---
import SectionHeading from "../ui/section-heading.astro";
---

<section id="dress-code" class="py-10 md:py-16 px-6 bg-white/80">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <SectionHeading cursive size="md">Ждем Вас!</SectionHeading>
    
    <p class="text-center text-lg max-w-md mx-auto mt-4 text-text/80">
      Будем благодарны, если при выборе нарядов на наше торжество вы придержитесь следующей палитры
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-3 md:gap-4 mt-8">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-dress-1 border border-white/50 shadow-sm"></div>
      <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-dress-2 border border-white/50 shadow-sm"></div>
      <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-dress-3 border border-white/50 shadow-sm"></div>
      <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-dress-4 border border-white/50 shadow-sm"></div>
      <div class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 rounded-full bg-dress-5 border border-white/50 shadow-sm"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
